{
  "stem": "1736.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, I must explain here that her brother, Chaim, was living in Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she got the message of what I was trying to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, she knew that I'm going to give it a go and try and get out of Germany with the eventual--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a code you were trying to give her--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a code.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That you were going to Israel without saying you were going to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We're speaking through the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You knew the phone call could be overheard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a type of language that was used not to-- not to spell it out, because, I mean, I was-- I would have given myself away if I would have said I want to escape.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she agreed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He listened in, and he said, OK, if she says that's fine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we then started making a few inquiries, and I must say he was helpful with that, and put us onto an address in Berlin that when we were going to go.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we just packed a little parcel for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The date had come, I advised my mother, and by pure coincidence, my late mother had asked for permission to leave Aken to visit Berlin, to fix up something, and it coincided on the day that-- I knew when she was going to be there and I left Hamburg with this friend of mine, and--",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Vitus.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "V-I-T-U-S.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mandelbaum.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we arrived in Berlin, and I met my mother at the station there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I met her at my aunt's place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Berlin.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had an aunt living there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother took me to the station when we were leaving.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
